

glossary {UPC} {Unidata Program Center}

glossary {IDV} {The Integrated Data Viewer}

glossary {Isosurface} {A type of display that shows a 3D surface for a given value}

glossary {Plan view} {A type of display that shows a horizontal surface.}

glossary {Bundle} {A bundle is an xml file that captures the state of the IDV application. 
                   It contains information about all data sources, displays, windows
                   and views.}


glossary {Color table} {A color table is a list of colors that allow one to map a
                       range of values to a range of colors.}

